OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FThe royal trip to the United States
OL,7,Fhas still not been officially
OL,8,Fconfirmed, but King Charles' state
OL,9,Fvisit to see Donald Trump should not
OL,10,Fbe cancelled, according to a senior US
OL,11,Fdiplomat.
OL,13,FThe US ambassador to the UK told a
OL,14,Fbusiness conference in London that it
OL,15,Fwould be a "very big mistake" for the
OL,16,FBritish government to ditch plans for
OL,17,Fthe King and Queen to travel to
OL,18,FWashington DC next month.
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
