CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FWarren Stephens, who was President
OL,7,FTrump's pick for UK ambassador, was
OL,8,Fasked about the planned visit at the
OL,9,Fend of April in a question-and-answer
OL,10,Fsession at the British Chambers of
OL,11,FCommerce conference.
OL,13,FHe was unable to confirm that King
OL,14,FCharles will make the trip but said:
OL,15,F"I think he will go and I think it
OL,16,Fwill be a very meaningful trip for
OL,17,Fhim."
OL,26,@yD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FAnswering a question from delegates
OL,7,Fabout whether it should be cancelled,
OL,8,Fgiven the current controversy
OL,9,Fsurrounding President Trump's war in
OL,10,FIran, Mr Stephens said: "I think that
OL,11,Fwould be a very big mistake."
OL,13,FBuckingham Palace has not announced
OL,14,Fthe King and Queen's visit, and
OL,15,Fneither has the White House, but ITV
OL,16,FNews understands it is scheduled to
OL,17,Ftake place in the last week of April.
OL,26,@sD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
