OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FIt is likely to involve all the
OL,7,Ftrappings of a US state visit to the
OL,8,FWhite House, including Guards of
OL,9,FHonour and a formal banquet with
OL,10,Fspeeches.
OL,12,FThe US Ambassador also said King
OL,13,FCharles has been asked to address both
OL,14,Fhouses of the US Congress while he is
OL,15,Fthere.
OL,17,FThe last time a British Monarch did
OL,18,Fthat was in 1991 when Queen Elizabeth
OL,19,Fspoke in Washington DC during a 12-day
OL,20,FUS state visit as a guest of President
OL,21,FGeorge HW Bush.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FKing Charles and Queen Camilla are
OL,7,Falso expected to visit New York later
OL,8,Fin the week.
OL,10,FThey are there to mark the 250th
OL,11,Fanniversary of US Independence, which
OL,12,Fthe nation is celebrating this year.
OL,14,FDonald Trump has previously said the
OL,15,FKing was coming "very soon" but the
OL,16,Fwar with Iran, which the US and Israel
OL,17,Fare prosecuting, has made the whole
OL,18,Fthing diplomatically uncomfortable for
OL,19,Fthe UK.
OL,26,@wD@QOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
