CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FThe location for state visits by the
OL,7,FBritish Monarch is decided by the
OL,8,Fgovernment of the day and reflects the
OL,9,FPrime Minister's priorities.
OL,11,FKing Charles, therefore, travels on
OL,12,Fgovernment advice, so it is not within
OL,13,Fhis gift to cancel the trip.
OL,15,FThat decision rests with Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
