OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FBut yet again, Donald Trump has lashed
OL,7,Fout at the British Prime Minister and
OL,8,Fthe UK response to the military
OL,9,Foperation in Iran led by the US and
OL,10,FIsrael.
OL,12,FMost recently, he called British
OL,13,Faircraft carriers "toys" and said
OL,14,F"don't bother" to send Royal Navy
OL,15,Fhelp, "we don't need it".
OL,26,@uD@SOUuD@XO]vD@AOUvD@NO]wD@GOUwD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
