PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FIf any such comments were made in
OL,7,Ffront of the King, it would be hugely
OL,8,Fembarrassing given Charles is the
OL,9,Fcommander in chief of the UK military
OL,10,Fand one of the aircraft carriers, HMS
OL,11,FQueen Elizabeth is named after the
OL,12,FKing's late mother.
OL,14,FPreviously, Trump said that among
OL,15,Fother things, that Starmer is "no
OL,16,FWinston Churchill".
