OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1774569807
OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FIf the war in Iran is still raging
OL,7,Fwhen the King visits the White House,
OL,8,Fit will put him in an awkward
OL,9,Fposition, given that the Sovereign is
OL,10,Fconstitutionally bound to remain
OL,11,Fimpartial and 'above politics'.
OL,13,FAnd there is always the risk of Donald
OL,14,FTrump uttering some unplanned words or
OL,15,Finsults about his European allies
OL,16,Fduring the King's time in the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
