OL,3,CCancelling King's US visit would be a
OL,4,C'mistake' says Trump's ambassador to UK
OL,6,FA senior British source told ITV News
OL,7,Frecently that the visit would go ahead
OL,8,Fno matter what Donald Trump says
OL,9,Fbecause the purpose of the King's
OL,10,Fvisit in America's 250th year was to
OL,11,Fhonour the people of the country
OL,12,Frather than the occupant of the Oval
OL,13,FOffice at this moment in time.
OL,15,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,16,Fweekly podcast about the royal family,
OL,17,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,18,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson...
